021) - Wrote backend services in Java and Python for e-commerce platform - Frontend development using React, Angular, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS - Database management with MySQL and PostgreSQL - Participated in agile scrum ceremonies and sprint planning EDUCATION Bachelor of Science in Computer Science - FAST NUCES Lahore (2015-2019) CGPA: 3.7/4.0 Relevant Coursework: Software Engineering, Machine Learning, Data Science, Database Systems, Web Development CERTIFICATIONS - AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Oracle Certified Java Professional - Google Certified Professional Data Engineer - Scrum Master Certified (CSM)'),(10,13,'BSCS - FAST',3.60,'Java','','Lahore','','2026-05-02 16:06:06',NULL),(11,14,'BSCS',0.00,'react','','karachi','','2026-05-03 00:13:34',NULL);
